//! Minimal perfect hash table for CSI dispatch routing.
//!
//! Maps `(intermediate_encoding, final_byte)` pairs to dispatch handler
//! identifiers using a multiply-add-shift hash whose parameters were
//! found by brute-force search and formally verified collision-free by
//! the z4 SMT solver.
//!
//! Hash function: `h(key) = ((key * A + B) >> C) % TABLE_SIZE`
//! where `key = (intermediate_enc << 8) | final_byte`.

